mannerpoints = "Manner Points (MP) are calculated based off of your performance in ALL Fountain of Manner League seasons. This includes wins, losses, how many seasons you've played, what group you were placed in, forfeits (as negative points), 2-0's, and playoff performance.\n\nWins are worth 12 points. Losses are worth 6 points. Forfeits are worth -12 points. 2-0's are worth 8 points. Playoff wins are worth 20 points. Playoff losses are worth 12 points. Playing in a season gets you 50 points. Group multipliers have a range of 1.0 - 1.2 of your total manner points."
